    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mb-6">Constants used: <strong>c</strong> = 299,792,458 m/s (speed of light in vacuum), <strong>h</strong> = 6.626 &times; 10<sup>&minus;34</sup> J&middot;s (Planck's constant).</p>

